<h1 id="自定义事件-子传父" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#自定义事件-子传父" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 自定义事件 子传父</h1>
<h3 id="app-vue" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#app-vue" aria-hidden="true">#</a> App.vue</h3>
<div class="language-vue line-numbers-mode" data-ext="vue"><pre v-pre class="language-vue"><code>（<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>template</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class="token attr-name">id</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>app<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>子传父<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>学生姓名为：{{stuName}}<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token comment">&lt;!-- 父传给子一个方法，子props调用方法做到子传父 --></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>Student</span> <span class="token attr-name">:getStudentName</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>getStudentName<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>Student</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>

    <span class="token comment">&lt;!-- 法一：父组件绑定一个自定义事件，v-on或@--></span>
    <span class="token comment">&lt;!-- &lt;School @mit.once="getSchoolName">&lt;/School> --></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>School</span> <span class="token attr-name">@mit</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>getSchoolName<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">@demo2</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>demo<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>School</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>

    <span class="token comment">&lt;!-- 法二：父组件绑定一个自定义事件,使用ref，灵活性强（不用在一开始就给子组件绑定自定义事件） --></span>
    <span class="token comment">&lt;!-- &lt;School ref="school">&lt;/School> --></span>
